OS		: Kali linux ARM
Device	        : RaspberryPi 3
IP Local	: 192.168.1.10 (Static)
Netmask       	: 24
IP Gateway	: 192.168.1.1

SETUP LOCAL SERVER
sudo apt update
sudo apt install apache2
ufw allow ‘Apache’
sudo service apache2 start

INSTALL MYSQL
## Add MariaDB APT repository ##
sudo apt -y install software-properties-common gnupg2
sudo apt-key adv --recv-keys --keyserver keyserver.ubuntu.com 0xF1656F24C74CD1D8
echo "deb [arch=amd64] http://mariadb.mirror.liquidtelecom.com/repo/10.6/debian bullseye main" | sudo tee /etc/apt/sources.list.d/mariadb.list
sudo apt update

## Confirm ##
apt policy mariadb-server

## Install MariaDB ##
sudo apt install dirmngr
sudo apt update
sudo apt install mariadb-server
systemctl start mysql
sudo mysql -u root -p
[no password]

## Start and enable mariadb service ##
sudo systemctl enable --now mariadb

## Secure MariaDB server ##
sudo mysql_secure_installation
-------------------------------------------------
Switch to unix_socket authentication [Y/n] n , 
Change the root password? [Y/n] y , 
Remove anonymous users? [Y/n] y , 
Disallow root login remotely? [Y/n] y , 
Remove test database and access to it? [Y/n] y ,
Reload privilege tables now? [Y/n] y , 
-------------------------------------------------

INSTALL PHP
## Add SURY PHP PPA repository ##
sudo apt -y install lsb-release apt-transport-https ca-certificates 
sudo wget -O /etc/apt/trusted.gpg.d/php.gpg https://packages.sury.org/php/apt.gpg
echo "deb https://packages.sury.org/php/ bullseye main" | sudo tee /etc/apt/sources.list.d/php.list

sudo apt install libapache2-mod-php
sudo apt install libphp-embed
sudo apt install php



*notes
Fix E: Package 'mysql-server' has no installation candidate
sudo apt install mariadb-server mariadb-client

Fix phpmyadmin not found after install
sudo ln -s /etc/phpmyadmin/apache.conf /etc/apache2/conf-available/phpmyadmin.conf sudo a2enconf phpmyadmin.conf sudo systemctl restart apache2



SIMPLE IP PUBLIC
echo $(wget -qO - https://api.ipify.org)
(your ip Public)
done

SETTING ROUTER
Port Forwarding

Name           : simpleServer
Protocol       : TCP And UDP
WAN Connection : Auto
LAN Host       : 192.168.1.10
WAN Port       : 80 OR Your Port
LAN Host Port  :80 OR Your Port


RESTART APACHE
sudo service apache2 restart
done
